OL,3,CMan in custody after arrest on
OL,4,Csuspicion of murdering Ann Widdecombe
OL,6,FA 26-year-old man is in custody for
OL,7,Fquestioning after he was arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of murdering former MP and
OL,9,FMEP Ann Widdecombe.
OL,11,FThe ex-Tory prisons minister was found
OL,12,Fdead at her home in Haytor on Dartmoor
OL,13,Fon Thursday after sustaining serious
OL,14,Finjuries.
OL,16,FMiss Widdecombe, who was 78, later
OL,17,Fbecame a Brexit Party MEP and
OL,18,Fsubsequently a Reform UK spokeswoman.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
