PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783820902
OL,3,CMan in custody after arrest on
OL,4,Csuspicion of murdering Ann Widdecombe
OL,6,FShe also found fame outside politics
OL,7,Fafter starring in Strictly Come
OL,8,FDancing and Celebrity Big Brother.
OL,10,FThe case of her death is "not being
OL,11,Ftreated as terrorism" and there is "no
OL,12,Finformation" at this time to suggest
OL,13,Fit was a "politically-motivated
OL,14,Fcrime", Devon and Cornwall Police said.
OL,16,FThe police force's Assistant Chief
OL,17,FConstable Matt Longman said the white
OL,18,FBritish suspect was arrested at an
OL,19,Faddress in Newton Abbot on Friday.
OL,26,@rD@ZOUsD@UO]sD@dOUtD@LO]uD@JOUvD@FO]
