OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783820902
OL,3,CMan in custody after arrest on
OL,4,Csuspicion of murdering Ann Widdecombe
OL,6,FPolice are remaining "open-minded"
OL,7,Fabout the motive for the attack, and
OL,8,Fsaid it was too early to comment on
OL,9,Fwhether the suspect was known to Miss
OL,10,FWiddecombe.
OL,12,FIn a statement on social media, Reform
OL,13,FUK leader Nigel Farage said the former
OL,14,FMP and MEP's death, and subsequent
OL,15,Fpolice murder investigation, was a
OL,16,F"terrible reflection on modern
OL,17,FBritain".
OL,26,@nD@VOUnD@bO]xD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
