OL,3,CMan in custody after arrest on
OL,4,Csuspicion of murdering Ann Widdecombe
OL,6,FConservative leader Mrs Badenoch said
OL,7,Fshe "really struggled to find the
OL,8,Fwords to say" following Miss
OL,9,FWiddecombe's death.
OL,11,F"I don't understand how someone could
OL,12,Fdo something so horrific to an elderly
OL,13,Fperson. It was a nasty, horrific
OL,14,Fattack and my heart is breaking for
OL,15,Fher family," she added.
OL,26,@oD@EOUpD@MO]sD@AOUwD@LO]
