OL,3,CMan in custody after arrest on
OL,4,Csuspicion of murdering Ann Widdecombe
OL,6,FMiss Widdecombe was a Conservative MP
OL,7,Fbetween 1987 and 2010 for the Kent
OL,8,Fconstituency of Maidstone, later
OL,9,FMaidstone and the Weald, and held
OL,10,Fseveral ministerial positions in Sir
OL,11,FJohn Major's government.
OL,13,FIn her post-Commons career, she
OL,14,Fappeared on the BBC's Strictly Come
OL,15,FDancing in 2010, partnered with Anton
OL,16,Fdu Beke, and survived until the
OL,17,Fcompetition's semi-finals thanks to
OL,18,Fthe public vote.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
