PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783820902
OL,3,CMan in custody after arrest on
OL,4,Csuspicion of murdering Ann Widdecombe
OL,6,FShe became a member of Mr Farage's
OL,7,FBrexit Party from 2019 and served as
OL,8,Fan MEP representing South West England
OL,9,Fin Brussels between 2019 and 2020.
OL,11,FShe later became immigration and
OL,12,Fjustice spokeswoman for Mr Farage's
OL,13,FReform UK and remained active in the
OL,14,Fmedia ` she appeared on TalkTV on
OL,15,FWednesday, the day before she was
OL,16,Ffound dead.
OL,18,FMiss Widdecombe was also due to be a
OL,19,Fguest on Channel 5's Matt Alright show
OL,20,Fon Wednesday afternoon, but did not
OL,21,Fappear, as first reported by ITV.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
