PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783820902
OL,3,CMan in custody after arrest on
OL,4,Csuspicion of murdering Ann Widdecombe
OL,6,FShe had exchanged messages with a
OL,7,Fresearcher from the show, but did not
OL,8,Frespond when they tried to contact her
OL,9,Fto join a Zoom call from home.
OL,11,FCalls and texts sent after the
OL,12,Fprogramme aired remained unanswered,
OL,13,FITV said, and the Channel 5 show's
OL,14,Fteam followed up with her agent later
OL,15,Fon Wednesday and on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
